data.description: ALL THE EXTRAS WRAPPED UP FOR YOU IN THIS PERFECTLY PERFECT HOME!! Owner has $32k in solar panels installed in 2021...SUPER EFFICIENT with virtually no electric bill at all. This Gorgeous Riverside home offers a brilliant floor plan that your family will LOVE!!! Features include an open concept kitchen with mocha cabinets, large granite island, stainless steel appliances, subway tiled backsplash, walk in pantry * flex space or office off entry * living area with wood burning fireplace * engineered wood flooring and tile * private en suite with lovely bathroom, garden tub, walk in shower, large closet, dual sinks and more * high ceilings* upgraded fixtures * foam insulation * covered patio * privacy fenced backyard * beautiful landscaping * sprinkler and security sys * community pool * storage building * all nestled on a corner lot!
